data.description:
SENSATIONAL ONE-OF-A-KIND--ONE OF THE FINEST SETTINGS IN TRILOGY! Huge, deep tranquil backyard on a NEARLY QUARTER-ACRE LOT. Over $100K spent between 2020-23 on the fully fenced backyard with HUGE TRAVERTINE TILE PATIO with GAS FIREPIT, large artificial turf PUTTING GREEN & your own beautiful botanic garden. Wide open WASH AND VIEWS on side of home. Welcoming front courtyard with travertine tile & custom steel gate. Huge open floor plan with views consists of the kitchen, great room, lounge area and dining area--an entertainer's dream--all with beautiful HARDWOOD PLANK FLOORS. The kitchen displays striking engineered stone on counters and on huge island with breakfast bar. Stainless built-in appliances with unique Samsung French-style refrigerator, GE Profile appliances. Premium staggered cabinets with soft close & rollouts, Blanco sink with touch faucet. Primary bath in the spacious master suite and guest bath feature engineered marble shower or tub/shower surround & countertops, framed mirrors & elevated toilets. Half bath with pedestal sink has elevated toilet. Popular Smart Space with LG washer & dryer is loaded with cabinets, has a sink and two work stations. Many outstanding upgrades include 9.1 kW PREPAID LEASED SOLAR, 20-in tile floors & upgraded carpet in bedrooms, higher baseboards, double doors on den, custom ceiling fans, 3 garage spaces (2+1 split) with epoxy floors, outdoor trash enclosure. SUNRISE & SUNSET VIEWS.

This home is located in award-winning gated, 55+ Trilogy at Vistancia with 5-star-resort style amenities at the 35,000 SF Kiva Club with indoor & outdoor pools, fitness center, day spa, cafe, billiards, meeting rooms, library, tennis courts, pickle ball, bocce ball, events & a plethora of activities to choose from. Outstanding Gary Panks-designed golf course is woven throughout the original part of the neighborhood. The Mita Club has additional outstanding community amenities. Easy access from Trilogy to the 303, shopping, restaurants, entertainment, Lake Pleasant & Paloma Park, Peoria's huge new community park loaded with amenities.
